thread.title_full: Key Tower returns to local ownership, with $267.5 million sale to Millennia Companies (photos)

author: Michelle Jarboe, The Plain Dealer
title: Key Tower returns to local ownership, with $267.5 million sale to Millennia Companies (photos)
text: The Millennia Companies of Valley View bought the 57-story office building, attached hotel and garage from Columbia Property Trust, Inc., in a sale that closed Tuesday.
